Last update: Nov 12th 2004

To build and install PyScintilla from source distribution:

1) Download latest version of Scintilla from <http://www.scintilla.org>
   Currently tested version is 162. 

2) Unpack the downloaded archive in the current direcory. 
   This will create direcory "scintilla" 
     Under linux:
     $> tar xfz scintilla-<version>.tar.gz 

     Under Windows:
     $> unzip scintilla-<version>.zip

3) Enter direcory "scintilla/gtk" and build Scintilla:
   $> cd scintilla/gtk
   $> make

3) Go back to the top level direcory and run setup.py:
   $> python setup.py install


